{
  "texts": [
    "In this case, Carlsen was misaligned with my goals.",
    "He didn't try to do what I wanted him to do.",
    "If AI is misaligned, it will tend to not do what we want it to do.",
    "In at least one respect, misaligned AI is not under our control.",
    "Given these clarifications, P3 states that, given the antecedent of the conditional and by 2100, some AI systems capable of disempowering humanity will pursue goals which differ from what their designers want them to be."
